  <div class="content">
    <p><a href="http://www.oracle.com/technology/products/jdev/howtos/1013/SpringwithJDev/index.html" target="_self">Getting Started With Spring 2.0 in Oracle JDeveloper</a> is a well illustrated OTN article by Shay Shmeltzer which shows how to set up JDeveloper to use the Spring framework, and then highlight some of the functionality in JDeveloper that can make your development experience with Spring more productive.</p>
