      <h2 class="title">
      <a href="/node/329" title="Tutorial: Introduction to Spring 2 and JPA">Tutorial: Introduction to Spring 2 and JPA</a>
    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Keith Donald on Fri, 2006-08-18 06:44        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p><a target="_self" href="http://www-128.ibm.com/developerworks/edu/j-dw-java-spring2-i.html?S_TACT=105AGX59&amp;S_CMP=HP-GR&amp;ca=dgr-jw17Spring2-JPA">Introduction to Spring 2 and JPA</a>, a developerWorks tutorial by Sing Li, shows's how to create web-based server applications from scratch using Spring 2.0. The persistence technology used is JPA.</p>
