    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Colin Sampaleanu on Mon, 2006-08-14 07:36        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_6 first last active"><a href="/presentations" rel="tag" title="A link to a technical article about Spring" class="active">Technical Article</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>In <a href="http://www.jroller.com/page/sjivan?entry=ajax_based_login_using_aceci" target="_self">Ajax based login using Acegi</a>, Sanjiv Jivan shows how to implement an Ajax based login to your web applications when using Acegi (Spring) Security.</p>
  </div>

